{
  "texts": [
    "For instance, the statement \"I passed a bill\" implicitly suggests a vote of affirmation.",
    "Our analysis found that only 1,198 (5.7%) of PolitiFact fact-checks explicitly mention \"vote,\" whereas the GPT-4o-mini model predicted Vote frames at nearly three times that amount.",
    "Although we observed numerous claims that evoked the Vote frame without explicitly using the word \"vote,\" additional research is needed to determine the true distribution of frames in factual claims.",
    "Similarity model selection.",
    "To retrieve relevant information for fact-checking, we first evaluated different semantic similarity models."
  ]
}